{
  "id": "69eaab1fac9e1e3c32eb5e28",
  "title": "自己有能感",
  "created": 1776986916,
  "updated": 1776987142,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69eaab1fac9e1e3c32eb5e28",
      "text": "自己有能感",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986916,
      "updated": 1776986916
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab2200000000006eb85a",
      "text": "from [幼児的万能感]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986916,
      "updated": 1776986917
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab2300000000006eb85b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986916,
      "updated": 1776986916
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab2600000000006eb85c",
      "text": "子供から大人になるにつれて、[幼児的万能感]が[[自己有能感]]に置き換わる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986918,
      "updated": 1776986954
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb85e",
      "text": "\t[幼児的万能感]：私は何でもできる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986958
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb85f",
      "text": "\t[[自己有能感]]：　私は[やればできる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986966
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb860",
      "text": "\t[コツコツ頑張ればできる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986974
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb861",
      "text": "  魔法のように立ち所に何かが降って湧くことはない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb862",
      "text": "  [銀の弾などない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb863",
      "text": " スーパーヒーロー　→　[スポ魂]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986984
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb864",
      "text": " [勤勉性]が身につく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986990
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb865",
      "text": " \t勉強、運動、友達との関係",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb866",
      "text": " \t学ぶ喜び",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb867",
      "text": " \t[達成欲求]を満たすようになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986994
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb868",
      "text": " \t\t意欲の源",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb869",
      "text": " \t[困難]から[安易に逃げない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987002
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb86a",
      "text": "   [責任感]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987005
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb86b",
      "text": "   [信頼]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987007
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb86c",
      "text": "   [技術的困難]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987008
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb86d",
      "text": "   [精神的困難]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987009
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb86e",
      "text": " 社会参加",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb86f",
      "text": " \t家族という社会",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb870",
      "text": " \t手伝い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb871",
      "text": " \t\t依存から一員へ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb872",
      "text": " \t\t世話される状態から協力する状態へ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb873",
      "text": " [幼児的万能感]を克服するためには、[失敗経験]と[成功体験]のどちらも必要",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987028
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb874",
      "text": " \t[失敗体験]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987031
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb875",
      "text": "   失敗体験があれば、自分の力量を知ることができる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb876",
      "text": "  \t失敗を受け入れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb877",
      "text": "  \tそこから成長できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb878",
      "text": "  [成功体験]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987033
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb879",
      "text": "   自分で何かをやると決めて、それに対して努力をして結果を出す",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb87a",
      "text": "   成果の大きさは関係なく、自分で何かを決めて行うことが重要",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb87b",
      "text": "  → [失敗経験]と[成功体験]の両方を経験することができれば、自然と「今の現状を受け入れて、努力する」ということの大切さを身に染みて感じる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776987050
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb87c",
      "text": "  → [幼児的万能感を克服]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaab3e00000000006eb87d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776986942,
      "updated": 1776986942
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabba00000000006eb880",
      "text": "[失敗経験から学ぶ姿勢が重要]の手前",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987066,
      "updated": 1776987079
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabc900000000006eb882",
      "text": "\t[自己有能感]：失敗経験から学ぶ姿勢を取るためのメンタリティ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987080,
      "updated": 1776987116
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabaf00000000006eb87e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987055,
      "updated": 1776987055
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabfd00000000006eb883",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987133,
      "updated": 1776987133
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabfe00000000006eb884",
      "text": "[[自己有能感]]を感じにくくなることもある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987133,
      "updated": 1776987138
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabfe00000000006eb885",
      "text": "\t世の中が便利すぎて自分の努力で成し遂げている感覚が得づらい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987133,
      "updated": 1776987133
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabfe00000000006eb886",
      "text": "\t\t数十年前と比べてみよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987133,
      "updated": 1776987133
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabfe00000000006eb887",
      "text": "\t[自給自足]→[[自己有能感]]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987133,
      "updated": 1776987142
    },
    {
      "id": "69eaabfe00000000006eb888",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776987133,
      "updated": 1776987133
    }
  ]
}